{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On a lonely stretch of road outside of Houma, Louisiana, is a gentlemen's club: <i>Heaven's Door</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263380/extras/hdmainmenu.jpg?t=1737606808\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One late Thursday night you are driving by, as you have a dozen times over a dozen recent Thursdays. This time, however, something tells you to park and head inside...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And the course of your life changes in ways you could not have imagined.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From the creators of <i>Bare Witness</i>, join us as we tell the story of a man with little left to lose, and nothing left to live for, who finds a bit of each in the most unlikely place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With nearly a dozen main love interests, branching storylines, and plenty of sexiness, we hope you'll find many reasons to return again and again to Heaven's Door. So find a seat, get your singles ready, and prepare for the ride of a lifetime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263380/extras/presplash_foreground.png?t=1737606808\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737606808","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263380/page.bg.jpg?t=1737606808","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263380/8fcadb0ff2b456eaeaa2ebf6cd20fa79c52dff70/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737606808","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263380/8fcadb0ff2b456eaeaa2ebf6cd20fa79c52dff70/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737606808","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,3,4,5],"notes":"Heaven's Door has sig